<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.9">
<l>nāṭāta malarnāṭi nāṭōṟu nāraṇaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>vāṭāta malaraṭikkīḻ vaikkavē vakukkiṉṟu</l>
<l>vīṭāṭivīṟṟiruttal viṉaiyaṟṟa teṉceyvatō</l>
<l>vūṭāṭu paṉivāṭā yuraittīrā yeṉatuṭalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is appointed to seek unsought blossoms every day</l>
<l>[and] place [them] under the unfading blossom feet of Nāraṇaṉ.</l>
<l>Playing release, sitting enthroned, what [good] will it do for cutting off [my] deeds,</l>
<l>o roaming chilly north wind, you being one that wears away my body?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
